systems in this state. The fact that the NLS1s NGC 4051 and\nMCG-6-30-15 do appear to show a power spectrum similar to that of the high/soft\nstate of Cyg X-1 may lend observational support to theoretical speculation that\nthe Hydrogen ionization disc instability does not operate in AGN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 May 2005 09:52:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 Aug 2005 10:43:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
